## Limitations

The findings are based on available online sources, which may not cover all aspects of the topic comprehensively. The search was limited to articles and reports accessible without subscription barriers, potentially excluding some academic or proprietary insights. Additionally, the dynamic nature of team dynamics means that the effectiveness of cohesiveness and diversity can vary significantly across different contexts and industries.

